doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title About Us
    link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap", rel="stylesheet")
    link(href="/styles/About.css", rel="stylesheet")

  body 
    include _header

    section.about-section
      .about-container
        h1.about-title About Us
        p.about-text
          | In moments of crisis, speed, clarity, and connection can make all the difference. Our platform is built to bring those elements together — empowering communities, responders, and individuals with instant access to critical support during emergencies.
          br
          br
          | Whether you're reporting a hazard, seeking help, or offering aid, we ensure every second counts.

      .card-container
        .card
          img(src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2965/2965567.png", alt="Fast Response Icon")
          h3 Fast Response
          p Our system ensures alerts are transmitted quickly to the right authorities and local responders to reduce damage and save lives.

        .card
          img(src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2601/2601979.png", alt="Real-Time Updates Icon")
          h3 Real-Time Updates
          p Stay informed with verified, up-to-the-minute notifications and emergency instructions — all in one place.

        .card
          img(src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1042/1042333.png", alt="Community Safety Icon")
          h3 Community Safety
          p We encourage everyone to participate — whether you're helping out or need assistance, we believe safety is a shared responsibility.

      .about-container(style="margin-top: 3rem; animation-delay: 1s;")
        p.about-text
          | We're not just a tool — we're a network. By bridging the gap between those in need and those who can help, we strive to build resilient communities ready to respond to any emergency.
          br
          br
          | Together, we can make safety accessible, responsive, and reliable — for everyone.

            
            


